                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151025-74-off434 t18151025-74-cd435"></join>, four bushels of oats, value 18 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18151025-74-victim603" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Bell
                  <interp inst="t18151025-74-victim603" type="surname" value="Bell"></interp>
