                     <interp inst="t18151025-74-person607" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was called, but the counsel for the prosecution declared he should ask him no question as he did not believe him worthy of credit; and expressed his surprise that he was not also put at the bar with the prisoner, as the wilful receiver of the stolen property.</p>
